Dialogue: 100,0:02:02.60,0:02:04.80,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}在狮子的鬃毛里有一个宝石人!\N{\rENG}There's a Gem inside of Lion's mane! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:04.82,0:02:05.70,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一个宝石人?\N{\rENG}A Gem? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:05.70,0:02:06.70,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}描述一下她\N{\rENG}Describe her. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:06.70,0:02:08.11,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}额 等一下\N{\rENG}Uh, hang on a sec. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:09.83,0:02:10.78,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 等等!\N{\rENG}Hey, wait! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:11.28,0:02:12.37,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她很高\N{\rENG}She's big. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:13.75,0:02:15.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈? 嘿 不要走!\N{\rENG}Huh? Hey, don't go! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:15.58,0:02:17.63,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她有彩虹色的头发和纹身\N{\rENG}With rainbow hair and tattoos. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:17.92,0:02:19.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}彩虹色的头发?\N{\rENG}Rainbow hair? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:19.92,0:02:21.46,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她的宝石是什么样的?\N{\rENG}What does her gem look like? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:21.67,0:02:23.34,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是个内陷的形状?\N{\rENG}It's...an innie? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:23.96,0:02:25.22,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不可能\N{\rENG}It can't be. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:25.23,0:02:26.38,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么不可能?\N{\rENG}Can't be what? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:26.59,0:02:28.22,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 带她出来\N{\rENG}Steven, bring her out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:28.70,0:02:29.43,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好哒\N{\rENG}Okay. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:35.61,0:02:37.44,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿! 朋友\N{\rENG}Hey! Little friend. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:37.44,0:02:37.81,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢!\N{\rENG}Ah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:38.23,0:02:39.15,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不要走!\N{\rENG}No, don't go! 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:39.50,0:02:43.07,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我好像迷路了 这里只有我们两个\N{\rENG}I believe I'm lost and there's no one here but us, 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:43.07,0:02:44.78,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以帮我一下怎么样?\N{\rENG}so how about a little help? 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:54.46,0:02:56.45,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇! 一个陌生人\N{\rENG}Wow! A total stranger. 
Dialogue: 100,0:02:57.83,0:03:00.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠...石榴\N{\rENG}Pearl...Garnet. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:00.75,0:03:03.09,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铋-必-斯...女母-姆!\N{\rENG}Bi-i-s...mu-u-th! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:03.09,0:03:05.30,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊哈哈哈! 你回来了!\N{\rENG}Ah ha ha ha! You're back! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:05.46,0:03:07.70,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇哦! 嘿!\N{\rENG}Whoa! Hey! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:07.70,0:03:10.11,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我认识的那个珍珠才不会跳进我的怀里\N{\rENG}The Pearl I know never jumps into my arms. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:10.18,0:03:11.72,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 谁家珍珠丢了?\N{\rENG}Hey, did somebody lose a pearl? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:12.10,0:03:13.18,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你属于谁?\N{\rENG}Who do you belong to? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:13.31,0:03:14.39,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁也不属于\N{\rENG}Nobody. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:14.39,0:03:15.72,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈哈\N{\rENG}Ha ha! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:15.93,0:03:18.06,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好了 好了 冷静下来\N{\rENG}All right, all right. Settle down. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:18.35,0:03:19.64,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看看是谁在说话\N{\rENG}Oh, you're one to talk. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:19.64,0:03:21.02,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 噢 抱歉\N{\rENG}Oh, oh, excuse me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:21.06,0:03:22.70,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是谁"们"在说话\N{\rENG}You're two to talk. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:24.70,0:03:25.78,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 冷静\N{\rENG}Hey, cool it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:26.11,0:03:27.44,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的红宝石性格显露出来了哦\N{\rENG}Your ruby is showing. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:27.70,0:03:29.20,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你去哪了?\N{\rENG}Where have you been? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:29.45,0:03:31.03,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们以为你被捕了\N{\rENG}We thought you'd been captured. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:31.28,0:03:33.28,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}或者更糟 被粉碎了\N{\rENG}Or, worse, shattered. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:33.70,0:03:35.66,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉碎我? 噗!\N{\rENG}Shatter me? Pssh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:35.87,0:03:39.00,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星不能在这颗宝石上留下任何划痕\N{\rENG}Homeworld couldn't lay a scratch on this Gem. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:39.04,0:03:40.17,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}咳咳!\N{\rENG}Ahem! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:40.46,0:03:41.33,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是谁?\N{\rENG}Who is this? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:41.54,0:03:44.04,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}大家 这是铋斯姆\N{\rENG}Guys, this is Bismuth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:44.04,0:03:46.21,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她是最早入队的宝石战士之一\N{\rENG}She's one of the original Crystal Gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:46.34,0:03:48.20,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 嘿 新成员!\N{\rENG}Oh, hey, new recruits! 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:48.55,0:03:49.59,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}欢迎加入\N{\rENG}Welcome aboard. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:49.59,0:03:51.38,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们永远不嫌紫晶太多\N{\rENG}We can always use more amethysts. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.05,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个肉丸子是谁?\N{\rENG}And who's this meatball? 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:54.55,0:03:55.56,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗨! 我是史蒂文\N{\rENG}Hi. I'm Steven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.64,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你刚才在我的狮子里 现在你在我的房子里\N{\rENG}You were in my lion and, now, you're in my house. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:58.27,0:03:59.81,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧 谢谢你收留我\N{\rENG}Well, thanks for having me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:03:59.93,0:04:01.65,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我不敢相信!\N{\rENG}I can't believe it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:02.94,0:04:04.27,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰说她在金字塔那一战中\N{\rENG}Rose said she lost track of you
Dialogue: 100,0:04:04.27,0:04:05.82,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}丢失了你的踪迹\N{\rENG}at the battle for the Ziggaurat. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:05.82,0:04:07.53,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她担心极了!\N{\rENG}She was worried sick! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:09.65,0:04:10.36,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等一下\N{\rENG}Wait. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:10.65,0:04:11.57,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰呢?\N{\rENG}Where is Rose? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:11.86,0:04:15.45,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗨 额 实际上 我是玫瑰的儿子\N{\rENG}Hi, um. Actually, I'm Rose's son. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:15.45,0:04:17.37,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她某种意义上变成了我\N{\rENG}She kind of turned into me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.54,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我有她的宝石 其他部分来自我爸爸\N{\rENG}Well, I have her gem. The rest is from my dad. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:20.70,0:04:21.71,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦\N{\rENG}Oh. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:21.71,0:04:23.04,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她在这\N{\rENG}There she is. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:23.90,0:04:24.96,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你...\N{\rENG}You...
Dialogue: 100,0:04:25.50,0:04:26.54,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你认识我吗?\N{\rENG}Do you know me? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:26.95,0:04:27.88,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}并不\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:27.88,0:04:29.12,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm so sorry. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:29.12,0:04:32.80,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰的选择不总是很容易理解 \N{\rENG}It's not always easy understand Rose's choices, 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:33.30,0:04:35.60,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是我们必须支持她\N{\rENG}but we have to stand behind them. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:36.05,0:04:39.43,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰真的变成了别人\N{\rENG}Rose really is somethin'else. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:40.77,0:04:42.39,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我是说看看这!\N{\rENG}I mean, look at this! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:42.39,0:04:44.69,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰真的变成了别人\N{\rENG}She really is somethin'else. 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:47.17,0:04:49.11,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇! 所有的事物都变了!\N{\rENG}Wow! Everything's changing! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:49.11,0:04:52.07,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们的基地现在是木制的了?\N{\rENG}And we're buildin'bases out of wood now?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:53.45,0:04:55.30,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是谁的坏点子?\N{\rENG}Whose terrible idea was this? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:55.30,0:04:57.03,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其他人呢?\N{\rENG}And where is everybody else? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:57.03,0:04:58.54,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}其他人?\N{\rENG}Everybody else? 
Dialogue: 100,0:04:58.70,0:05:00.79,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是啊 剩余的宝石战士!\N{\rENG}Yeah, the rest of the Crystal Gems! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:01.25,0:05:03.33,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}疯狂的老花边 比格斯 雪花\N{\rENG}Old Crazy Lace, Biggs, Snowflake. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:06.88,0:05:07.63,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不\N{\rENG}No. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:07.70,0:05:08.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不可能!\N{\rENG}No way! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:09.25,0:05:11.13,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们刚刚...还在这\N{\rENG}We were...just here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:11.67,0:05:12.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我失踪了多久?\N{\rENG}How long was I out? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:13.00,0:05:15.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}大约有5300年了\N{\rENG}It's been about 5, 300 years. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:16.30,0:05:18.47,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们 宝石战士们 \N{\rENG}We, the Crystal Gems, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.60,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}成功拯救了地球\N{\rENG}were able to save the Earth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:20.85,0:05:23.35,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是我们是仅存的反叛军了不是吗?\N{\rENG}But we're all that's left of the Rebellion, huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:25.05,0:05:26.98,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 别呀珍珠\N{\rENG}Aw, come on, Pearl. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:27.27,0:05:29.94,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道我看不得你哭\N{\rENG}You know I can't take it when you cry like that. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:30.44,0:05:31.45,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}抱歉\N{\rENG}I'm sorry. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:31.45,0:05:33.99,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不 不需要道歉\N{\rENG}No. No need to apologize. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:34.32,0:05:36.32,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星对地球最后的攻击\N{\rENG}Homeworld's final attack on Earth
Dialogue: 100,0:05:36.61,0:05:39.12,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}毁了所有的宝石战士\N{\rENG}wiped out all of the Crystal Gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.70,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰设法保护了石榴和我\N{\rENG}Rose was able to protect Garnet and myself
Dialogue: 100,0:05:41.79,0:05:43.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}看起来 \N{\rENG}and, by the looks of it, 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:43.08,0:05:44.77,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她也保护了你\N{\rENG}she was able to protect you as well. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:45.23,0:05:46.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Ah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:46.21,0:05:49.25,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我就知道那些母星的精英心理扭曲\N{\rENG}I knew those Homeworld elites were twisted. 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:49.54,0:05:51.21,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们粉碎了我们多少人?!\N{\rENG}How many of us did they shatter?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:51.43,0:05:53.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}老花边? 比格斯!\N{\rENG}Crazy Lace? Biggs! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:53.84,0:05:55.54,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}雪花?!\N{\rENG}Snowflake?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:55.54,0:05:58.05,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果我当时在这 我--能阻止他们!\N{\rENG}If I was there, I--I could've stopped it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:05:58.16,0:06:00.02,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}他们从没停止过尝试\N{\rENG}It's not like they've stopped trying. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:00.02,0:06:01.55,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你说啥?\N{\rENG}What's that? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:01.55,0:06:03.88,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星从未停止对地球的监视\N{\rENG}Homeworld still hasits eyes on this planet. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:03.88,0:06:05.95,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们不断粉碎他们的阴谋\N{\rENG}We continue to thwarttheir plans, 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:05.95,0:06:07.18,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一遍又一遍\N{\rENG}over and over. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:07.19,0:06:09.09,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是他们还是不断卷土重来!\N{\rENG}But they just keep\Ncoming back! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:09.09,0:06:11.39,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对 他们超想我们挂掉\N{\rENG}Yep, they want us, bad. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:11.39,0:06:12.42,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不错\N{\rENG}Good. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:12.43,0:06:14.03,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我还以为没有第二次机会\N{\rENG}I thought I wouldn't get another chance
Dialogue: 100,0:06:14.03,0:06:16.43,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}来让那些高层昏庸们见识下谁是老大!\N{\rENG}to show those upper crusts who's boss! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:16.43,0:06:21.53,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们来让他们看看惹恼水晶战士们后会有什么后果!\N{\rENG}Let's show 'em what happens when you mess with the Crystal Gems. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:23.27,0:06:24.67,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}棒\N{\rENG}Yeah. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:24.67,0:06:26.47,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铋斯姆 母星的宝石人\N{\rENG}Bismuth, the Gems on Homeworld
Dialogue: 100,0:06:26.47,0:06:29.27,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}数量比我们多到不知道哪里去了\N{\rENG}outnumber us by a huge amount. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:29.28,0:06:31.31,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有他们的科技水平\N{\rENG}And their technology far surpasses
Dialogue: 100,0:06:31.31,0:06:34.01,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}也远超地球上的所有\N{\rENG}anything we have available on Earth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:36.15,0:06:37.88,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这也能算新闻?\N{\rENG}What else is new? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:37.88,0:06:39.72,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}石榴 记不记得那次你和我\N{\rENG}Garnet, remember when you and I
Dialogue: 100,0:06:39.72,0:06:42.59,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}打掉了一个营的石英战士?\N{\rENG}took on a battalion of Quartz soldiers? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:42.59,0:06:44.99,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}走出战场那时候 咱们身上的宝石\N{\rENG}We walked out with our stones shining brighter
Dialogue: 100,0:06:44.99,0:06:46.66,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}比战斗前还要闪亮\N{\rENG}than when we walked in. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:46.66,0:06:49.58,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我可是记得咱们打掉了三个营\N{\rENG}As I recall, it was three battalions. 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:49.58,0:06:52.98,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有珍珠 记得那次咱俩停住了那艘登陆舰?\N{\rENG}And, Pearl, remember when we stopped that drop ship? 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:52.98,0:06:55.98,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}瞧瞧当时那只闪玉脸上的表情!\N{\rENG}I'll never forget the look on that Nephrite's face
Dialogue: 100,0:06:55.98,0:06:58.10,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你直接就把她从那鸡窝里拽出来了!\N{\rENG}when you pulled her out of the cockpit! 
Dialogue: 100,0:06:58.10,0:07:00.14,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我记得\N{\rENG}I know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:00.14,0:07:02.37,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当时她超尴尬的\N{\rENG}How embarrassing for her. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:02.38,0:07:03.47,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈--哈!\N{\rENG}Ha-ha! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.88,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}现在咱们从落下的地方重新开始吧!\N{\rENG}So let's pick up where we left off! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:05.88,0:07:07.85,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}锻造车间 出发!\N{\rENG}To the forge! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:07.85,0:07:08.88,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}耶!\N{\rENG}Yay! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:08.88,0:07:10.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}锻造车间 出发!\N{\rENG}To the forge! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:10.08,0:07:11.85,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喂 啥是锻造车间啊\N{\rENG}Yo, what's a forge? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:18.98,0:07:21.65,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}多么令人怀念啊!\N{\rENG}That brings back memories, huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:21.65,0:07:22.98,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是锻造车间?\N{\rENG}Is this the forge? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:22.98,0:07:24.05,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还没到呢\N{\rENG}Not yet. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:24.05,0:07:26.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}跟我来\N{\rENG}Follow me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:27.89,0:07:29.85,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}到锻造车间了吗\N{\rENG}Is this the forge? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:29.86,0:07:32.72,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 别问我啊 我又没来过\N{\rENG}Ugh. Don't ask me. I've never been here before. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:32.73,0:07:35.36,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯 自打铋斯姆失踪之后\N{\rENG}Well, since Bismuth was gone, 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:35.36,0:07:37.26,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们也没来这里的理由了\N{\rENG}we've had no reasn to come back here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:37.26,0:07:40.73,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可不是吗 这个地方离了我什么都不是\N{\rENG}Let's just say this place ain't the same without me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:40.73,0:07:42.17,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么意思\N{\rENG}What does that mean? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:42.17,0:07:43.70,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}紫晶! 你觉得那是什么意思?\N{\rENG}Amethyst! What do think you that means? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:43.70,0:07:44.87,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也不造啊 宝\N{\rENG}I don't know, dude. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:44.87,0:07:47.24,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}今天是我第一次见这只宝石人\N{\rENG}I've never even seen this Gem before today. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:47.24,0:07:49.67,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星把我们打得稀里哗啦\N{\rENG}We took a huge blow from Homeworld. 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:49.68,0:07:52.94,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是今天我们又重新"铋"入正轨了!\N{\rENG}But, now, we're back in Bismuth ( business). 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:54.08,0:07:55.81,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她真会讲笑话\N{\rENG}She's got jokes! 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:55.81,0:07:57.88,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是锻造车间了?\N{\rENG}Is this the forge? 
Dialogue: 100,0:07:57.88,0:07:59.15,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}差一点\N{\rENG}Not quite. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:07.68,0:08:08.80,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗒—哒!\N{\rENG}Ta-da! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:08.80,0:08:10.83,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇哦 瞧瞧这绝赞的大门!\N{\rENG}Wow. Now, that's an entrance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:10.83,0:08:12.80,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}超棒! 铋斯姆!\N{\rENG}Bravo, Bismuth! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:14.03,0:08:16.80,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊! 铋斯姆!\N{\rENG}Aaaah! Bismuth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.47,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇!\N{\rENG}Whoa! 
Dialogue: 600,0:08:16.80,0:08:18.47,Hint,NTP,0,0,0,,从尺寸看这把剑应该源自"数码宝贝"的奥米加兽
Dialogue: 100,0:08:18.47,0:08:20.97,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}和之前一点没变啊\N{\rENG}It's just like I remember it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:20.97,0:08:23.47,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这里热得和烤炉一样\N{\rENG}It feels like an oven in here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:23.48,0:08:25.38,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你以为这就算热了?\N{\rENG}You think it's hot now? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:25.38,0:08:27.55,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对啊 烤炉一样热\N{\rENG}Yeah, like an oven. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:28.68,0:08:32.65,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下还会更---热呢!\N{\rENG}Well, it's about to get way hotter! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:39.56,0:08:41.79,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}赞!\N{\rENG}Ah, cool! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:41.79,0:08:42.63,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈!\N{\rENG}Ooh. Hah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:42.63,0:08:47.16,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没什么比淋个岩浆浴更能焕发精神的了\N{\rENG}Nothing like a hot lava bath to get into a working mood. 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:50.30,0:08:52.83,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 你在这里都做些什么?\N{\rENG}Uh, what, exactly, do you do here? 
Dialogue: 100,0:08:52.83,0:08:56.78,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星使唤我们这些铋斯姆来建造尖塔和庙宇\N{\rENG}Homeworld used us Bismuths to erect spires and temples
Dialogue: 100,0:08:56.78,0:08:59.68,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}供那些宝石精英们享受\N{\rENG}for the Gem elites to enjoy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:01.98,0:09:05.15,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是玫瑰告诉我们可以主宰自己的命运\N{\rENG}But Rose taught me that my life was my own, 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:05.15,0:09:06.95,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可以自己选择\N{\rENG}that I could choose
Dialogue: 100,0:09:06.95,0:09:08.25,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}去做\N{\rENG}to do
Dialogue: 100,0:09:08.25,0:09:10.19,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}自己想做的所有事\N{\rENG}whatever I wanted. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:12.22,0:09:14.72,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以我选择做这个\N{\rENG}So I chose this. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:15.70,0:09:18.73,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铋斯姆 你是做...武器的?\N{\rENG}Bismuth, you make...weapons?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:18.73,0:09:19.86,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不错!\N{\rENG}That's right! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:19.87,0:09:22.73,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我打造了叛军的所有武器\N{\rENG}I outfitted the entire Rebellion. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:22.74,0:09:25.57,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}每一件水晶战士们用的武器\N{\rENG}Every material weapon used by the Crystal Gems
Dialogue: 100,0:09:25.57,0:09:28.04,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}都是在这里制作的\N{\rENG}was made right here in this forge. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:28.04,0:09:31.07,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下 那个东西还在吗\N{\rENG}Wait. Is it still here? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:31.08,0:09:33.34,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊哈! 还在!\N{\rENG}Aha! Yes! 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:33.35,0:09:33.45,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给\N{\rENG}Here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:34.57,0:09:36.54,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个东西能辅助你出拳\N{\rENG}Something to pack a little extra punch. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:36.54,0:09:39.41,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你为什么不试试三叉戟呢\N{\rENG}And why don't you try a trident. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:39.41,0:09:41.82,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 铋斯姆 没必要这么客气\N{\rENG}Oh, Bismuth, you shouldn't have. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:42.12,0:09:43.59,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没啥大不了的\N{\rENG}It's no big deal. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:43.59,0:09:45.30,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我做这些东西好长时间了 自打...\N{\rENG}I was working on them since before...
Dialogue: 100,0:09:46.11,0:09:48.42,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 现在给你们也无妨\N{\rENG}Well, may as well give them to you now. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:48.91,0:09:50.06,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等多久都值得\N{\rENG}It was worth the wait. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:50.76,0:09:53.63,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 和你们打交道"铋"然开心啊\N{\rENG}Hey, it's a pleasure doing Bismuth with you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:53.63,0:09:56.63,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铋斯姆超搞笑的\N{\rENG}Bismuth is so funny. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:56.64,0:09:58.04,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不好说\N{\rENG}I don't know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.64,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她一个梗用了两次了\N{\rENG}Same joke twice? 
Dialogue: 100,0:09:59.64,0:10:01.20,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嗯 她如果用这个梗三次\N{\rENG}Well, it'll be really funny
Dialogue: 100,0:10:01.21,0:10:02.54,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那才叫搞笑\N{\rENG}if she does it a third time. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:02.54,0:10:03.61,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好吧\N{\rENG}Right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:03.61,0:10:05.51,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起 这个很不好说\N{\rENG}Sorry, I--I don't know. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:05.51,0:10:08.28,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我意思是 她是最初的水晶战士之一\N{\rENG}I mean, she's one of the original Crystal Gems
Dialogue: 100,0:10:08.28,0:10:10.11,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是却没人提到过她?\N{\rENG}and no one ever mentioned her to me, 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:10.12,0:10:11.45,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}甚至玫瑰都没说过?\N{\rENG}not even Rose? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:11.45,0:10:13.62,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不觉得有点 呃\N{\rENG}Don't you think that's a little bit, uh.. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:13.62,0:10:15.22,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可疑吗?\N{\rENG}suspicious? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:15.22,0:10:18.02,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是有点奇怪了\N{\rENG}I guess that is a little strange. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:18.02,0:10:20.26,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}嘿 小家伙 别以为我把你忘了\N{\rENG}Hey, deep cut, don't think I forgot about yo. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:20.26,0:10:21.89,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你的武器是啥\N{\rENG}What you packin'? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:21.89,0:10:23.59,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 这个老物件而已\N{\rENG}Oh, this old thing? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:23.60,0:10:25.00,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 哇\N{\rENG}Oh, wow. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:25.01,0:10:27.11,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}-怎么了?-额\N{\rENG}-What is it?-Well...
Dialogue: 100,0:10:27.12,0:10:29.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没见过别的石英用这种鞭子的\N{\rENG}Not every Quartz can make a whip like this. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:29.33,0:10:30.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}介意我拿来看下吗?\N{\rENG}You mind if I take a look? 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:30.84,0:10:31.74,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}随便观赏咯\N{\rENG}Knock yourself out. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:31.74,0:10:34.04,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等下! 我有个主意\N{\rENG}Hold on! I've got an idea. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:35.64,0:10:39.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}给 有了这个 你破坏力能提升不少\N{\rENG}Here. With this, you can really do some damage. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:43.38,0:10:45.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦液 宝贝儿!\N{\rENG}Aw, yeah, baby. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:45.08,0:10:48.29,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铋斯姆坠棒!\N{\rENG}Bismuth's the best! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:48.29,0:10:50.22,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星把我们当作泥土看待\N{\rENG}Homeworld treats us like dirt
Dialogue: 100,0:10:50.22,0:10:52.42,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为我们不像那些精英一般闪耀\N{\rENG}because we don't shine like the elites. 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:52.42,0:10:54.36,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但现在水晶战士们卷土重来了\N{\rENG}But the Crystal Gems are back
Dialogue: 100,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.69,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们会给那些钻石们\N{\rENG}and we'll give those Diamonds
Dialogue: 100,0:10:55.69,0:10:57.73,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一些颜色看看!\N{\rENG}another taste of what's coming! 
Dialogue: 100,0:10:58.73,0:11:01.03,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好 现在给我瞧瞧你们有什么能耐 战士们!\N{\rENG}Now, show me what you got, soldiers. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:02.44,0:11:05.00,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 我认为这红蓝宝石\N{\rENG}Unh! I think the power couple's
Dialogue: 100,0:11:05.00,0:11:06.64,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}失去了她们的力量!\N{\rENG}losin'their spark. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:07.77,0:11:09.14,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}谁是下一个?\N{\rENG}Who's next? 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:09.14,0:11:10.44,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈啊—啊—啊!\N{\rENG}Ha ha-a-a! 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:10.44,0:11:12.48,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}珍珠 我可没让你\N{\rENG}Pearl, I don't recall
Dialogue: 100,0:11:12.48,0:11:14.71,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}带给我一支矛\N{\rENG}asking you to bring me a spear. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:15.78,0:11:17.91,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你可不会喜欢我如何把它带给你\N{\rENG}You won't like how I give it to you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:17.92,0:11:19.45,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哇哦 激光?\N{\rENG}Ah! Lasers? 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:19.45,0:11:20.95,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么时候变成这样的?\N{\rENG}When did that happen? 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:20.95,0:11:22.22,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什....\N{\rENG}Wha...?! 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:22.22,0:11:26.12,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我要破坏你的"铋"需品!\N{\rENG}I'm gonna wreck your Bismuth. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:28.26,0:11:29.93,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你很有创意\N{\rENG}Very creative. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:29.93,0:11:32.93,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦耶 我想我还是挺不错的\N{\rENG}Yeah, I guess I am pretty great. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:32.93,0:11:34.26,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就对了!\N{\rENG}That's right! 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:34.27,0:11:35.53,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们是力量的象征!\N{\rENG}We are powerful. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:35.53,0:11:37.17,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们是重要的代表!\N{\rENG}We are important. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:37.17,0:11:38.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们是!\N{\rENG}We! are! 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:38.84,0:11:40.17,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}水晶!\N{\rENG}the Crystal
Dialogue: 100,0:11:40.17,0:11:42.94,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}--战士!\N{\rENG}Ge-e-e-e-e-ms! 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:42.94,0:11:46.48,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}史蒂文 快来让我看看你有什么能耐\N{\rENG}Steven, come down and show me what you're made of! 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:46.48,0:11:50.21,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢 我会的 但这对我来说太激烈了\N{\rENG}Uh, I would, but this is a little intense for me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:50.22,0:11:52.35,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这可是我们在战斗之前\N{\rENG}But it's a ritual for us Crystal Gems
Dialogue: 100,0:11:52.35,0:11:53.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所需的试炼\N{\rENG}to spar before battle. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:53.75,0:11:55.62,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}事实上 我有一些更好的\N{\rENG}Well, actually, I have some rituals
Dialogue: 100,0:11:55.62,0:11:57.39,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}训练方法\N{\rENG}I like a little better. 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.82,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢是吗?\N{\rENG}Oh, yeah? 
Dialogue: 100,0:11:58.82,0:12:00.16,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}让我瞧瞧\N{\rENG}Let me see 'em. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:11.97,0:12:15.57,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么...\N{\rENG}Wha...? 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:26.72,0:12:29.59,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}传说中的充满力量的恶魔之刃\N{\rENG}The powerful, legendary demon blade, 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:29.59,0:12:31.32,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}被村正附体...\N{\rENG}possessed by Muramasa. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.46,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}一旦我拥有了这把恶魔之刃 我就能成为\N{\rENG}With this demon blade, I will be
Dialogue: 100,0:12:33.46,0:12:35.73,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}世界上最强大的战士!\N{\rENG}the most powerful fighter in all the world! 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:35.73,0:12:38.06,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不! 孤刃 不要使用它!\N{\rENG}No, Lonely Blade! Don't use it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.06,0:12:38.91,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}什么?\N{\rENG}What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:38.91,0:12:40.48,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果那把刀真有无穷的力量 \N{\rENG}If that thing's got infinite power, 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:40.48,0:12:42.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}孤刃肯定使用它啊 \N{\rENG}then, of courseLonely Blade should use it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:42.85,0:12:44.38,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这肯定说得通\N{\rENG}It just makes sense. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:44.38,0:12:45.95,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不需要说通 \N{\rENG}It doesn't have to make sense. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:45.95,0:12:47.72,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这只是演戏而已\N{\rENG}It's entertainment. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:48.49,0:12:49.41,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}无穷的...\N{\rENG}Infinite...
Dialogue: 100,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.88,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}力量!!!\N{\rENG}powe-e-e-e-r! 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:52.41,0:12:54.46,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}铋斯姆今晚你可以在这里休息 \N{\rENG}Bismuth, you can chill out here tonight
Dialogue: 100,0:12:54.46,0:12:56.86,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你想的话你还能睡一觉\N{\rENG}and...sleep, if you want to. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:56.87,0:12:57.96,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道吗\N{\rENG}You know what? 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:57.97,0:12:59.40,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我决定试一试\N{\rENG}I think I'll give it a try. 
Dialogue: 100,0:12:59.40,0:13:01.97,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我喜欢水晶战士的这些新惯例\N{\rENG}I like these new Crystal Gem rituals. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:03.24,0:13:05.30,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你知道的 通常我遇上一个新的宝石\N{\rENG}You know, usually, when I meet a new Gem, 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:05.31,0:13:07.44,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她们通常都试图干掉我 跟她们混熟\N{\rENG}they try and kill me and it takes me forever
Dialogue: 100,0:13:07.44,0:13:08.98,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}简直要用一辈子时间\N{\rENG}to become friends with them. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:08.98,0:13:11.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我的意思是 我很高兴你能加入我们\N{\rENG}I guess I mean I'm really glad you're here. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:11.85,0:13:13.11,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我也是\N{\rENG}Me, too. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:13.12,0:13:14.48,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我很高兴能再有一次机会重来\N{\rENG}Glad to have another chance. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:14.48,0:13:16.48,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}那明天\N{\rENG}So, tomorrow, you gonna show me
Dialogue: 100,0:13:16.48,0:13:18.05,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你要向我展示你在战场上有什么本事吗?\N{\rENG}what you goton the battlefield? 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:18.05,0:13:20.35,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哦 我是可以\N{\rENG}Oh, I mean, I-I would, 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:20.36,0:13:22.72,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不过我的武器大多都是防御用的\N{\rENG}but, most of my weapons are for defense. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:22.72,0:13:24.56,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}噢! 除了那一个\N{\rENG}Oh, except for one. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:28.76,0:13:30.63,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰的剑\N{\rENG}Rose's sword. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:30.63,0:13:32.67,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我最好的作品\N{\rENG}My finest piece of work. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:32.67,0:13:34.43,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你制造了它?\N{\rENG}You made this? 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:34.44,0:13:37.38,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你真的不记得了 对吧\N{\rENG}You really don't remember, huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:38.48,0:13:41.61,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰石英改变了我的一生\N{\rENG}Rose Quartz changed my life. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:42.66,0:13:45.43,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我刚来到地球时认为这里不过是另一个殖民地\N{\rENG}I came to Earth thinking this was just another colony. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:45.43,0:13:47.58,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}建造竞技场训练那些精英的战士\N{\rENG}Build another arena for important fighters to fight in, 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:47.58,0:13:51.09,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}建造尖塔给重要的冥想者去思考\N{\rENG}build another spire for important thinkers to think in, 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:51.09,0:13:52.50,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然后 我遇见了她\N{\rENG}and then, I met her. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:52.93,0:13:56.48,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她只是一名石英战士 诞生于这片土地\N{\rENG}Just another Quartz soldier, made right here in the dirt, 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:56.48,0:13:58.19,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但她却与众不同\N{\rENG}but she was different. 
Dialogue: 100,0:13:58.19,0:14:01.51,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}因为她选择了一条不同的道路\N{\rENG}And she was different because she decided to be. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:01.52,0:14:04.68,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她问我 什么是我想去创造的\N{\rENG}And she asked me what I wanted to build, 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:04.69,0:14:06.22,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}而我以前从未听过这样的话\N{\rENG}and I'd never heard that before. 
