Dialogue: 100,0:14:08.69,0:14:13.56,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但是玫瑰为我们打开了新的大门\N{\rENG}other than what they are, but Rose opened our eyes. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:13.56,0:14:16.60,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}大家总是告诉我我的母亲有多么优秀\N{\rENG}Everybody always tells mehow great Mom was. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.27,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我感觉自己永远比不上她\N{\rENG}I just don't feel like Ican ever measure up to her. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:20.67,0:14:22.10,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我真是不敢相信\N{\rENG}I can't believe this, 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:22.10,0:14:26.24,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我会在这里鼓励玫瑰的...\N{\rENG}that I'm the one givingthe pep talk to Rose's...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:26.24,0:14:27.51,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}玫瑰的?\N{\rENG}Rose's...? 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:27.51,0:14:28.61,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}儿子\N{\rENG}Son. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:28.61,0:14:29.84,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对\N{\rENG}Right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:29.85,0:14:31.25,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你是与众不同的\N{\rENG}You are different. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:31.25,0:14:32.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是重点\N{\rENG}That's what's so exciting. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:32.75,0:14:35.52,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你不需要像玫瑰石英一样\N{\rENG}You don't have to be like Rose Quartz. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:35.52,0:14:37.22,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能够成为比她更优秀的人\N{\rENG}You can be someoneeven better. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:37.22,0:14:39.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你能够做你自己\N{\rENG}You can be you. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:39.75,0:14:40.99,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}还有你知道吗\N{\rENG}And you know what? 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:40.99,0:14:43.26,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你理应得到更好的武器\N{\rENG}You deserve an even better weapon. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:45.49,0:14:48.63,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我设计这把剑为的是一场公平的较量\N{\rENG}I designed this swordfor a fair fight. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:48.99,0:14:53.07,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}它可以瞬间穿透宝石人的身体\N{\rENG}It can cut through a Gem's physical form in an instant! 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:53.07,0:14:56.94,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但不能破坏宝石本体\N{\rENG}Destroying the body, but never the Gem. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:56.94,0:14:58.37,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好厉害\N{\rENG}Cool. 
Dialogue: 100,0:14:58.37,0:14:59.74,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}然而\N{\rENG}But...
Dialogue: 100,0:14:59.74,0:15:02.21,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星从不公平对待战争\N{\rENG}Homeworld doesn't fight fair. 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:02.21,0:15:04.78,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这就是我们需要不同战略的原因\N{\rENG}That's why we need a different strategy. 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:06.05,0:15:08.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}喔 哇\N{\rENG}Ohh. Whoa. 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:12.76,0:15:15.76,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我之前在做一个能够改变战争局势的武器\N{\rENG}I was working on a weapon thatwould've been a gamechanger. 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:15.76,0:15:18.33,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}母星知道怎么一击必杀\N{\rENG}Homeworld knows how to hit us where it counts, 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:18.33,0:15:21.20,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}但我们可以做到她们能做到的一切 甚至更好\N{\rENG}but we can do everythingthey can do, and better. 
