Dialogue: 100,0:15:30.17,0:15:31.27,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这是什么?\N{\rENG}What is it? 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:31.27,0:15:34.57,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我叫它"断裂极限"\N{\rENG}I call it a Breaking Point. 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:34.58,0:15:36.34,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}赞! 它能做什么?\N{\rENG}Cool! What does it do? 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:36.34,0:15:37.68,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}好好瞧着吧\N{\rENG}Just watch. 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:37.68,0:15:38.98,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈!\N{\rENG}Hah! 
Dialogue: 100,0:15:55.46,0:15:58.23,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}听好了 你们这些母星的昏君\N{\rENG}Listen up, you Homeworld upper crusts! 
