Dialogue: 100,0:16:01.17,0:16:02.97,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}战士!\N{\rENG}Gems! 
Dialogue: 100,0:16:04.11,0:16:05.24,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Unh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:16:11.91,0:16:13.81,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}所以 你怎么看?\N{\rENG}So, what do you think? 
Dialogue: 100,0:16:13.82,0:16:15.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你......你粉碎了它\N{\rENG}Y-You shattered it. 
Dialogue: 100,0:16:15.75,0:16:17.15,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}没错!\N{\rENG}That's right! 
Dialogue: 100,0:16:17.15,0:16:19.42,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这个神器可以一眨眼的瞬间\N{\rENG}One shot from this baby will shatter any Gem
Dialogue: 100,0:16:19.42,0:16:22.26,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉碎星系中任何一个宝石\N{\rENG}in the galaxy, in the blink of an eye. 
