Dialogue: 100,0:17:07.48,0:17:08.62,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你说什么?\N{\rENG}What? 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:08.62,0:17:09.75,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为什么不行?\N{\rENG}Why not? 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.92,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}粉碎宝石 \N{\rENG}Shattering Gems, 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:11.92,0:17:14.29,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}做了这个我们和母星的人不是没有区别了吗?\N{\rENG}wouldn't that make us the same as Homeworld? 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:14.29,0:17:15.97,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}当然有!\N{\rENG}Of course not! 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:15.97,0:17:18.93,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我们粉碎他们是因为我们拥有正义的理由与目的!\N{\rENG}We'd be shattering them for the sake of our cause, 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:18.93,0:17:21.20,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为了守护我们的盟军! 我们的朋友!\N{\rENG}to protect our allies, our friends, 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:21.20,0:17:24.50,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}为了让所有的宝石从母星的暴政中获得自由!\N{\rENG}to free all Gems from Homeworld's tyranny! 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:24.50,0:17:25.68,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}可它...\N{\rENG}It's just, it--
Dialogue: 100,0:17:25.68,0:17:28.00,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}这不是一个宝石战士会去做的\N{\rENG}it's not what a Crystal Gem would do. 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:28.00,0:17:31.07,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不用告诉我一个宝石战士会去做些什么\N{\rENG}Don't tell me what a Crystal Gem would do. 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:31.07,0:17:34.18,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我这个宝石战士名副其实\N{\rENG}Nobody's more Crystal Gem than I am. 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:34.18,0:17:36.98,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}如果你不用它 那么就我用\N{\rENG}If you won't take it, I'll just use it myself. 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:36.98,0:17:41.18,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}不行! 没有人能用它!\N{\rENG}No! No one is using it! 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:42.32,0:17:45.09,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}对不起 铋斯姆 但这不对\N{\rENG}I'm sorry, Bismuth, but it's not right. 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:47.12,0:17:50.06,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}她也曾如此说过\N{\rENG}That's exactly what she said. 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:50.06,0:17:51.19,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}哈?\N{\rENG}Huh? 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:51.19,0:17:55.40,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就如同你这般说的\N{\rENG}That's exactly what you said. 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:55.40,0:17:56.53,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}呃 呃嗯...\N{\rENG}Uh, uh...
Dialogue: 100,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.70,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}是你对吧 玫瑰?\N{\rENG}It is you, isn't it, Rose? 
Dialogue: 100,0:17:58.70,0:18:01.27,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你-你到底在说什么?\N{\rENG}Wha-What are you talking about? 
Dialogue: 100,0:18:01.27,0:18:03.20,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}别骗我\N{\rENG}Don't lie to me. 
Dialogue: 100,0:18:03.21,0:18:05.67,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你在隐瞒了一切后 \N{\rENG}You can't expect me to believe you now, 
Dialogue: 100,0:18:05.68,0:18:07.54,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就不要指望我再相信你了\N{\rENG}after you lied about everything? 
Dialogue: 100,0:18:07.54,0:18:09.44,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}你隐藏了你的新形态 \N{\rENG}You're lying about this new form, 
Dialogue: 100,0:18:09.45,0:18:13.08,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}就像你向她们隐瞒着我的事!\N{\rENG}just like you lied to the others about me! 
