Dialogue: 100,0:18:20.49,0:18:21.66,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}啊!\N{\rENG}Uh! 
Dialogue: 100,0:18:21.66,0:18:22.99,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}等等! 铋斯姆!\N{\rENG}Wait! Bismuth! 
