Dialogue: 100,0:18:29.73,0:18:33.74,Normal Dialog Text,NTP,0,0,0,,{\rCHS}我曾经在这儿告诉你成功的秘诀 但你拒绝了\N{\rENG}I offered you the secret to victory, and you refused. 
